
#도커 네트워크 설정 아래 에러 발생 때문에
ERROR: Verifying runner... failed                   runner=t1_yi6s1C status=couldn't execute POST against http://localhost/ap
i/v4/runners/verify: Post "http://localhost/api/v4/runners/verify": dial tcp 127.0.0.1:80: connect: connection refused
PANIC: Failed to verify the runner.



docker network create gitlab-network
docker network connect gitlab-network gitlab
docker network connect gitlab-network gitlab-runner


## 도커에서 띄웠을 경우

gitlab-runner register  --url http://gitlab  --token glrt-t1_yi6s1Cf-5gU9NWeE86yd
                              이부분 도커 네임으로 지정해줘야됨 localhost 하면안됨

